Maritime Bulletin Daily Nov 04 – 05
05 Nov 2019, 06:13 by Mikhail Voytenko
Accidents• Tanker aground, Indonesia• Cargo ship and tanker collided in Jeju Strait• General cargo ship under tow• Aframax tanker attacked in Gulf of Guinea UPDATE attack confirmed, 4 kidnapped• Oil spill in Bremen• Aground and Not Under Command vessels Worldwide Alerts (2 ships)
